</IN>
<LP>
   DALLAS -- Caspen Oil Inc. named a new chairman and chief
executive in an organizational shuffle that also involved a
stock swap between its parent, Caspen PLC, and Churchill
Technology Inc., based in Lakewood, Colo.
   U.K.-based Caspen PLC exchanged half of its 70% stake in
