<LP>
   Pier 1 Imports Inc. said it achieved record sales and
earnings in its first quarter ended June 2.
   The Fort Worth, Texas, specialty retailer recorded net
income of $7.7 million, up 15% from the $6.7 million reported
in the period ended May 27, 1989. Per-share net, after
